{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Enter a place where darkness reigns and pure evil thrives.</h2><br>It's an ordinary nightshift for Sergeant Aaron until he receives a distraught radio call for help. A routine investigation quickly spirals into a fight for survival when you come face to face with pure evil.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989930/extras/01_House-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1730206067\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A GLIMPSE INTO THE TERROR</h2>From Fire Emergence utilises the tried and tested third person over the shoulder view point. Players will experience the chilling atmosphere as they see and guide Sergeant Aaron through eerie environments. Each step intensifies the suspense, heightening the feeling of vulnerability and the sense of being pursued by an unknown malevolence, creating a tense and immersive experience.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989930/extras/Stables_1-ezgif.com-resize-border.gif?t=1730206067\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FIGHT TO SURVIVE</h2>Terrifying monsters will stop at nothing to bring about your demise and end your progress. Use your limited resources wisely to fight off the determined evils looking to end your life.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989930/extras/RiveRun_1-ezgif.com-resize-border.gif?t=1730206067\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PREPARE TO FACE YOUR FEARS</h2>Hunt for resources and tools that will help you to solve puzzles and gather better equipment.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989930/extras/Lockpick_1-ezgif.com-resize-border.gif?t=1730206067\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989930/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730206067","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i